MATCH (m:Movie)<-[:CAST_FOR]-(p:Person)
RETURN m.title AS movie, count(p) AS cast_size
ORDER BY cast_size DESC
LIMIT 5

question: Name the top 5 production companies that have produced movies with a runtime longer than 150 minutes.
cypher:
MATCH (c:ProductionCompany)-[:PRODUCED_BY]-(m:Movie)
WHERE m.runtime > 150
RETURN c.name AS company, count(*) AS num_movies
